1
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:12,260
英文：Listen to the tape, then answer this question.
中文：听录音，然后回答问题。

2
00:00:14,189 --> 00:00:16,600
英文：Why was the mother embarrassed?
中文：妈妈为什么尴尬？

3
00:00:18,719 --> 00:00:25,879
英文：Last week, my four-year-old daughter, Sally, was invited to a children's party.
中文：上周，我四岁的女儿萨莉应邀参加了一个儿童聚会。

4
00:00:25,980 --> 00:00:29,640
英文：I decided to take her by train.
中文：我决定乘火车带她去。

5
00:00:30,859 --> 00:00:35,899
英文：Sally was very excited because she had never travelled on a train before.
中文：萨莉很兴奋，因为她以前从未坐过火车。

6
00:00:36,829 --> 00:00:42,759
英文：She sat near the window and asked questions about everything she saw.
中文：她坐在窗边，问她所看到的一切。

7
00:00:43,780 --> 00:00:49,479
英文：Suddenly, a middle-aged lady got on the train and sat opposite Sally.
中文：突然，一位中年女士上了火车，坐在萨莉对面。

8
00:00:50,559 --> 00:00:52,179
英文：Hello, little girl!
中文：你好，小姑娘！

9
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:53,439
英文：She said.
中文：她说。

10
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:58,320
英文：Sally did not answer, but looked at her curiously.
中文：萨莉没有回答，只是好奇地看着她。

11
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:04,659
英文：The lady was dressed in a blue coat and a large, funny hat.
中文：这位女士穿着一件蓝色外套，戴着一顶又大又滑稽的帽子。

12
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:13,079
英文：After the train had left the station, the lady opened her handbag and took out her powder compact.
中文：火车离开车站后，这位女士打开手提包，拿出粉盒。

13
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:16,640
英文：She then began to make up her face.
中文：然后她开始化妆。

14
00:01:17,459 --> 00:01:20,079
英文：Why are you doing that?
中文：你为什么这么做？

15
00:01:20,900 --> 00:01:22,280
英文：Sally asked.
中文：萨莉问。

16
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:28,039
英文：To make myself beautiful, the lady answered.
中文：为了让自己变得漂亮，这位女士回答。

17
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:33,000
英文：She put away her compact and smiled kindly.
中文：她收起粉盒，慈祥地笑了。

18
00:01:33,780 --> 00:01:37,899
英文：But you are still ugly, Sally said.
中文：但你还是很丑，萨莉说。

19
00:01:38,659 --> 00:01:43,840
英文：Sally was amused, but I was very embarrassed.
中文：萨莉很开心，但我很尴尬。

